Data set of appointed judges

Source: R/official.R
appointed_judges.Rd

The appointed_judges dataset contains information on the start and end periods of the appointed judges. The cutoff date for all of them is April 3, 2024, which note a real ending date but it is the moment in which I stopped collecting data.

Usage

appointed_judges

Format

A data frame with three variables:

name

Name of the judge

start

Start Date

end

End Date

Examples

  appointed_judges
